### Component 9: Background Scheduler

#### [NEW] [services/scheduler.py](file:///c:/Users/Keerthi Sridhar/Desktop/GAURDX/services/scheduler.py)
APScheduler jobs:
- Process raw data в†’ features (every 5 seconds)
- Run ML inference (every 5 seconds)
- Compute health score (every 5 seconds)
- Check alert conditions (every 10 seconds)
- Model retraining check (every 1 hour)

